                    <span style="font-size: 10px; background: #F0FDFA; color: #0f766e; border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 8px; font-weight: 600;">May 10, 2026</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 10px; color: #9CA3AF;">Hall C</span>
